SQL_STMT_U.val: select s.id, s.report_currency, rownum page_row from (select distinct r.id, r.report_currency from pc_portfolio_base b inner join performance_report r on b.pere_id = r.id where instrument_id = ~1 and r.id>=~2 and b.calc_date between to_date(~4,'YYYYMMDD') and to_date(~5,'YYYYMMDD') order by r.id) s where rownum <=~3
